            .hero-actions
                a.btn-primary(href="/brain") Open Explorer
                a.btn-ghost(href="/info") More Info
            .hero-meta
                span.hero-meta-item Browser-based
                span.hero-meta-item 20+ regions
                span.hero-meta-item Real-time interaction
        .hero-panel
            h2.panel-title What you can do
            ul.panel-list
                li Rotate, highlight, and inspect individual regions
                li Apply cross-sections by axis and depth
                li Compare circuitry across different addictive disorders
                

    .home-features
        article.feature-card
            h3.feature-title Region-Level Clarity
            p.feature-copy Click any structure to isolate it and understand its role in the full brain model.
        article.feature-card
            h3.feature-title Fast Visual Feedback
            p.feature-copy Switch presets and immediately see where activity is concentrated or reduced.
        article.feature-card
            h3.feature-title Built For Discussion
            p.feature-copy Use the view as a shared visual when explaining behavior and mental load.

